title: uTorrent and BitTorrent WebUI Installer
description:
This nifty little batch utility installs the WebUI to programs such as uTorrent and BitTorrent.

The code will copy the webui.zip file to the uTorrent or BitTorrent folder in your %AppData% folder.

The reason this is 1MB is because I included my logo with this release.

I wrote all of this using Notepad++, this program really helps when
programming!

Read LICENSE for licensing info
If you want to install the WebUI for BitTorrent, run BitTorrent.bat
If you want to install the WebUI for uTorrent, run uTorrent.bat


-uGot

ENJOY!!!
